|ProdCode        = BEJ311
|LineColor       = 97979F
}}
|Viewers         = 1.14
|ShortSummary    = With her Bolivian cocaine connection destroyed, Teresa makes a deal with her sworn enemy Camila. Cortez is targeted. Teresa works to free George from his imprisonment. Camila is trusted with a once-traitorous piece of technology, though it's uncertain if she's aware of its presence. James contemplates leaving Teresa and the business and having realized her mistakes, she begs him to stay.
|ProdCode        = BEJ312
|LineColor       = 97979F
}}
|Viewers         = 1.22
